<H1><A NAME="SECTION0213800000000000000000">
3.38 OETranslation</A>
</H1>
<dl><dd><pre class="verbatim">
OETranslation : public OETransBase
</pre></dl>

<P>
This object is one of the molecular transformation base classes which
derive from <code>OETransBase</code> and work with <code>OETrans</code>.

<P>
<dl><dd><pre class="verbatim">
OETranslation(const double* vec)
OETranslation(const float* vec)
OETranslation(double dx, double dy, double dz)
OETranslation(float dx, float dy, float dz)

//arithmetic operators
OETranslation &amp;operator += (const OETranslation &amp;rhs)

//data access
void GetTranslation(double *vec) const
void GetTranslation(float *vec) const

OETransBase *CreateCopy() const
</pre></dl>

<P>
This <code>OETransBase</code> object stores a Cartesian molecular translation.

<P>

